parameters.name: PortRangeListId
parameters.description:
The ID of the port list.

>  If the port list is associated with other resources, you cannot delete the port list. You must disassociate the port list from the resources and then delete the port list.

parameters.name: RegionId
parameters.description: The region ID of the port list. You can call the [DescribeRegions](~~25609~~) operation to query the most recent region list.
